I'll generally design for 1024, but with the proviso that the site isn't
rendered completely unusable at 800x600 - so things might be a little
cramped at lower resolutions, but it is still possible to find what you're
looking for.

I also advocate resolution-dependent layouts (if you can't manage
fluid/elastic):

http://www.themaninblue.com/writing/perspective/2006/01/19/

Matthew.
